<HEAD>Syria Assures Shultz Of Efforts To Gain Higgins' Release</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Shultz</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By NICK LUDINGTON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>DAMASCUS, Syria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
