said. <PERSON> Leyton </PERSON> directed his fire at <LOCATION> El </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Salvador </LOCATION> because that country had requested the emergency OAS session. `` This forum is being used like a political circus,'' <PERSON> Leyton </PERSON> screamed.
