ths after <PERSON> Hsu </PERSON> had left for the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, but Taiwanese officials said he helped organize it. In September 1986, <PERSON> Hsu </PERSON> organized a U.S.-based Taiwanese group, the <ORGANIZATION> Democratic </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Progressive </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Party </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Overseas </ORGANIZATION> that is affiliated with <LOCATION> Taiwan </LOCATION>'s opposition <ORGANIZATION> Democratic </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Progressive </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Party </ORGANIZATION>.
